author: sussman
msg: Entry add/del flag logic actually works now.  Phew.
(fold_entry):  correctly merge the incoming flag state into the entry;
we interpret the integer as a *command* in this routine, honoring the
clear bits.
(normalize_entry):  make the entry's attribute hash *exactly* match
the state flags, ignoring clear bits.
(internal_fold_sync): handle special case where interpret_changes()
might deliberately remove the entry.
